data.title: Service was terrible
data.text: We went on a Friday night before the dinner rush with 2 small children. The person taking the order must have been new as the accuracy of this order was not good . The delivery of our food took more than 10 minutes . One sandwich was not correct, the fries were cold, one kids meal didn't have a toy, the frosty ordered was not delivered. I fought the most important things but if I had done a drive thru this would have been a disaster . Please be sure to double check your order before leaving the counter or window and don't come with small children.
